    <description><![CDATA[<h1>DdlUtils</h1>

<h2>1.功能</h2>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; XWorker的DDL模型框架。</p>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 各种DDL相关的模型可以以<strong>child</strong>的方式注册到<strong>xworker.db.ddlutils.DdlUtils</strong>模型下，DDL模型需呀继承<strong>xworker.db.ddlutils.DdlUtil</strong>。</p>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; DdlUtil模型可以根据需要重写以下方法：</p>

<ul>
	<li><strong>void create(DataSource dataSource)</strong><br />
	执行创建。<br />
	&nbsp;</li>
	<li><strong>void alter(DataSource dataSource)</strong><br />
	执行修改。<br />
	&nbsp;</li>
	<li><strong>void drop(DataSource dataSource)</strong><br />
	执行删除。&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
</ul>

<h2>&nbsp; &nbsp;2.使用方法</h2>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在模型编辑器里通过DDLUtils菜单执行相关功能。</p>]]></description>&#xd;
    <en_description><![CDATA[<h1>DdlUtils</h1>

<h2>1. Function</h2>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; XWorker's DDL model framework. </p>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Various DDL-related models can be registered to the <strong>xworker.db.ddlutils.DdlUtils</strong> model in the manner of <strong>child</strong>. DDL models are required. Inherit <strong>xworker.db.ddlutils.DdlUtil</strong>. </p>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The DdlUtil model can rewrite the following methods as needed:</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>void create(DataSource dataSource)</strong><br />
Perform creation. <br />
&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>void alter(DataSource dataSource)</strong><br />
Perform the modification. <br />
&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>void drop(DataSource dataSource)</strong><br />
Perform deletion. &nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
</ul>

<h2>&nbsp; &nbsp;2. How to use</h2>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Perform related functions through the DDLUtils menu in the model editor. </p>]]></en_description>&#xd;
